新聞，結果釀成激烈爭吵，你知我好霸道唔會畀人講嘢㗎啦，愈鬧愈嘈，當時我情緒好激動爆喊叫停，但嗌極都無人肯收聲，真係唔知點算好，唯有撼頭埋牆自殘，撼到後腦起『樓』嚇親屋企人。」</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔夠人講就自殘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n幾撚on9先做得出"},{"pid":"f5ae2dc6cdc74c6e6e301dc5f1de9612eb148e05","tid":1573462,"uid":15259,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T04:28:13.000Z","msg":"咁明目張膽放攻擊性武器起頭上面<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4BAaJb2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4BAaJb2.jpg&h=3c6c83bb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n只有一個方法可以有效打擊藍屍<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1570141\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1570141</a>"},{"pid":"a6fee114671f5ae98e6b4cce458f2ac866aa4f3a","tid":1573462,"uid":279810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T04:35:00.000Z","msg":"啊 ......"}]}